<br>
Back in SoV, I made a big trade for a swiftblade of zek,<br>
from our resident high end guild. I recently sold it off,<br>
to get a weapon that would hold aggro better.<br>
<br>
Asking for advice from the warrior community.<br>
I've gathered some infos from various sites,<br>
and checked back a bunch of pages here, but <br>
I couldn't find any similar post.<br>
<br>
Old Combo was Swiftblade of Zek / Frostbringer,<br>
but i used then (currently use) Narandi's Lance,<br>
even while MT, because it simply aggros more.<br>
<br>
Of course most people have a lot to say about<br>
a MT using a 2h weapon, but as most have seen,<br>
the swiftblade is in essence a non-aggro weapon,<br>
while the lance procs very often, getting me all the<br>
taunt I need.<br>
<br>
The top 3 droppable taunt weapons I can seem to find,<br>
barring a SOD/BOC, which is unattainable, are:<br>
Fleshgrinder / Wavecrasher / Frostbringer<br>
<br>
I would like, if possible your thoughts on these 3,<br>
the best possible aggro combination, or perhaps<br>
something I may have overlooked.<br>
<br>
Please keep in mind I am unguilded, so am unable <br>
to attain a weapon such as Willsapper, which can <br>
be quite easy to obtain with even a small guild behind you.<br>
<br>
thanks in advance,<br>
